ing: 1 tablespoon unsalted natural peanut butter, or more to taste
des: "This smoothie is a great meal replacement, pre-workout drink, or even just a bomb snack."
ins: Blend almond milk, ice cubes, banana, coffee, protein powder, honey, and peanut butter in a blender on low speed. Gradually turn speed up to high and blend until smooth, 20 to 30 seconds.
